CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 3, 1951, pg. 22 reads: "Food From The Gods - At the completion of installation formalities of Alpha Omicron Lambda Chapter of Alpha Phi Alpha recently, this hungry group of brothers and their guests partook of a sumptuous repast prepared by the famous caterer, Roberta Bailey Lewis...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twelve women, five crouched down pointing to floor inscribed Alpha Phi Alpha, in Alpha Phi Alpha house for installation ceremonies, 3046 Centre Avenue
